{"tid":1314380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［擺明吹風向］721前哨升LV戰 - 光復沙田 即時討論區","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:22:46.000Z","uid":274839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e490259051ef83fd3a5b04d646b45b9af94b505a","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:49:04.000Z","msg":"開Post時即時資訊<br />\n<br />\n1）獅子山隧道公路已布重防，請轉東行使用大老山，或青山公路<br />\n2）新城市已有旗手準備<br />\n<br />\n支援資訊<br />\n<br />\n【沙田休息站】<br />\n<br />\n1. 沙田平安福音堂<br />\n地址：沙田瀝源街7號沙田娛樂城1樓B<br />\n－禮堂作休息、安靜禱告之用。如需任何支援、代禱、關心，亦可隨時與當值牧者同工傾談。<br />\n－開放至晚上7時<br />\n<br />\n2. 沙田浸信會瀝源座堂<br />\n地址：沙田瀝源街1號<br />\n－休息、情緒支援、祈禱站之用。提供洗手間、飲水、小食、充電。<br />\n－開放至晚上8時30分<br />\n<br />\n3. BEANS Coffee （沙田分店）<br />\n地址：新城市中央廣場 (Home Square) 5樓503號舖<br />\n－戶外區將闢作公眾休息區並免費為公眾添加飲用水<br />\n－下午3時起開放<br />\n<br />\n4. （新增）<br />\n信義會沙田多元化金齡服務中心<br />\n地址：沙田瀝源邨貴和樓123號地下<br />\n- 設立休息站、提供洗手間、飲水小食及情緒支援<br />\n-下午4時-8時開放<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n你以為今日係和理非？有狗的地方就會有混亂發生<br />\n你唔衝，人地都會上電吠你<br />\n<br />\n倒不如準備好自己，拎EXP升下LV仲好<br />\n<br />\n樓主尋日出完POST下左度火後決定今日繼續發夢，各位夢境內相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dae30b932261c3e4fb3e570ce1471ce60e0664","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:54:52.000Z","msg":"樓主私人資訊：<br />\n<br />\n1）大圍人開始多，今日人數應該會多過尋日<br />\n2）記得帶非黑色衫，以及出事後即時掉衫掉Gear<br />\n3）留意現場風向，睇準幾時係散水大限，唔好送頭<br />\n4）新城市「一定會」出賣你地，班狗今日「一定會」出椒。<br />\n5）兄弟爬山，和理非的咁多位唔好阻住勇武做野就得。<br />\n6）必要時自己做埋自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家加油，沙田必須光復！"},{"pid":"1c9116ef6e5a0708c4abef2f0e8c26c5e82f6329","tid":1314380,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d1fb87705da2f631ac680f786e71359121852d","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512770fd6dc308fea8c275c38caa76188e563470","tid":1314380,"uid":272300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e53ec43920e45bf4e1ae35aa0cb3bc98dfbd0b9d","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"風繼續吹"},{"pid":"e1ffc154dcb473fc88a411580421eaea35644797","tid":1314380,"uid":87062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9bfb153c3175d864ad8447868ed0feb742c766e","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"853afdd6c382b4356d0bdb8f88e2e99c1b76000f","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c1e5d682462e2a982755f090f61bb220b15461bd","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"Pysh"},{"pid":"05f39a718d462a67d04f6978586c39b8c2389a71","tid":1314380,"uid":255871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c59ffc9675cb27202b5b90339888c7604e5da58","tid":1314380,"uid":274839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n現場live （蘋果）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/889496828082620/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F889496828082620%2F&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1